This directory contains derivative works based on the following
open-source components. The original license terms apply to each
component as indicated below.

Modifications by Alejandro Fernandez Camello (2025):
  x86 SSE SIMD intrinsics rewritten to native RISC-V Vector (RVV)
  intrinsics (<riscv_vector.h>), making the code VLEN-agnostic.
  Automated widening via LLM-driven pipeline (src/widen.py).
  zlib dependency in main.c replaced with standard C file I/O.

